to the point it's too late to back out.

396
00:32:54,500 --> 00:32:55,290
Chakkrit.

397
00:32:56,130 --> 00:32:56,810
Yes?

398
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:58,670
Nosy!

399
00:33:00,340 --> 00:33:02,100
Understood, Boss.
I'll shut up now.

400
00:33:04,280 --> 00:33:06,530
I don't know who the person
