404
00:33:51,270 --> 00:33:52,790
The elevator's here.
This way, Boss.

405
00:33:53,270 --> 00:33:53,830
Huh?

406
00:33:54,170 --> 00:33:55,110
Who's the boss here?

407
00:33:56,040 --> 00:33:57,050
This way, Boss.

408
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,139
Then last night...

409
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:30,699
Who was that guy?!

410
00:34:36,050 --> 00:34:37,530
This guy...

411
00:34:41,130 --> 00:34:42,440
Not him...

412
00:34:45,650 --> 00:34:47,010
This guy?

413
00:34:51,620 --> 00:34:53,300
