422
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:23,140
Good morning.

423
00:35:23,170 --> 00:35:25,220
Would you like to check out now?

424
00:35:25,330 --> 00:35:27,340
Oh, no, I'd like to

425
00:35:27,950 --> 00:35:29,570
