434
00:35:51,210 --> 00:35:52,690
But this room is priced at

435
00:35:52,730 --> 00:35:55,420
18,900 baht per night.

436
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:59,930
18,900 baht.

437
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:05,620
I still haven't made
the most out of the room I booked!

438
00:36:05,940 --> 00:36:08,250
I have yet to invite anyone for a stay.

439
00:36:08,470 --> 00:36:10,980
If I were to book a new room,

440
00:36:11,010 --> 00:36:13,380
I might as well invite
the whole town for a stay.

441
00:36:14,570 --> 00:36:17,040
But I can assure you
the view is absolutely wonderful.

442
00:36:17,140 --> 00:36:19,080
It overlooks the hotel's back garden

443
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:21,340
