448
00:36:32,750 --> 00:36:35,480
For beverages, they still
have to be ordered through room service.

449
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:36,780
We sincerely apologize.

450
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:43,560
Please give me a moment.

451
00:36:50,340 --> 00:36:52,100
