a resort up the hill.

460
00:37:36,640 --> 00:37:38,740
It's called 'Phusangdao.'

461
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:41,030
Oh, my goodness.
That resort is located up the hill.

462
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:43,080
You'll get to see fog and stars
the entire time you're there.

463
00:37:43,250 --> 00:37:44,280
As for a tent,

464
00:37:44,310 --> 00:37:47,060
it only starts at 400 baht a night.

465
00:37:48,180 --> 00:37:49,730
400 baht?

466
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,570
Do they serve wine there?

467
00:37:51,630 --> 00:37:52,850
Of course, they do.

468
00:37:52,890 --> 00:37:54,990
They have their own tea farm
within the resort.

469
00:37:55,020 --> 00:37:55,680
And they serve

470
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:58,350
tea wine, their signature beverage.

471
00:37:58,670 --> 00:38:00,820
If you're interested,
you can learn more there.

472
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,370
[Phusangdao]

473
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,230
400 baht a night.

474
00:38:09,110 --> 00:38:09,890
Alright!

475
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:11,810
At least, I still got my rental car.

476
00:38:13,170 --> 00:38:14,170
